content:
Make key data in repeater widgets stand out by adding conditional formatting rules to text, numbers, charts, or images. For example, highlight countries with opportunity amounts less than 3 million dollars.

To customize dashboard widgets:
Create and Edit Analytics Dashboards

In the dashboard designer, select the repeater widget, click Edit Repeater Content.
Select the widget that you want to add the conditional formatting rule to and, then under Conditional Formatting, click Add Rule.
Add a rule to an existing text widget in the repeater by modifying the dashboard JSON.

Select the reference column to base the conditional formatting rule on and the coloring method to use. Preview your changes and save your dashboard.
title: Conditional Formatting in CRM Analytics
